  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.5.0-alpha03\" data-text=\"Version 1.5.0-alpha03\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.5.0-alpha03</h3>\n<p>October 2, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.collection:collection-*:1.5.0-alpha03</code> is released. Version 1.5.0-alpha03 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/0431b84980e97d6bafdfda7c9038bc4d9529564f..b6ae8d0a0e8cd803f7b84f30101eda1af4f1d6b6/collection\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Kotlin version update to 1.9 (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I1a14ce236e70bdc55f94afd42ead44587018c097\">I1a14c</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>External Contribution</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Forward <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">contains</code> to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">containsKey</code>. Thanks Jake Wharton! (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I9362b30782b97561d810b09e9746df96fac3625c\">I9362b</a>)</li>\n<li>Add container builders for scalar-specialized collections. Thanks Jake Wharton! (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I13179cbd2665dfbd1a1a1c97091df0e14954bb14\">I13179</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/0431b84980e97d6bafdfda7c9038bc4d9529564f..b6ae8d0a0e8cd803f7b84f30101eda1af4f1d6b6/collection"
